#. type: Title =
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Regions: Deleting control points\n"
msgstr "領域: 調整点の削除\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:5
msgid "[7 of 10](Regions-Inverting.html)"
msgstr "[7 of 10](Regions-Inverting.html)"

#. type: Plain text
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:8
msgid ""
"The shape of regions in LightZone can be adjusted at any time. This includes "
"deleting control points that are no longer needed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "To delete a control point from a region:\n"
msgstr "調整点を削除するには:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"Click the Regions button in the [tool bar](Tools-Controls.html).  (The "
"region kind buttons will appear to the right of the tool bar and the regions "
"for the tool will become visible on your photo.)"
msgstr "[ツール バー](Tools-Controls.html)で領域ボタンをクリックします。(The region kind buttons will appear to the right of the tool bar and the regions for the tool will become visible on your photo.)"

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"![image](images/Region-Delete_Point-en.png) Double-click the region that you "
"want to delete a control point from. (The control points will become "
"visible.)"
msgstr "![image](images/Region-Delete_Point-en.png) Double-click the region that you want to delete a control point from. (調整点が見えるようになります。)"

#. type: Bullet: '3.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"Control-click Right-click on the control point you want to delete: a menu "
"will pop up."
msgstr "調整点の上で右クリックまたは Ctrl-クリックすると、メニューがポップアップします。"

#. type: Bullet: '4.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid "Select Delete Point."
msgstr "「点を削除」を選択します。"

#. type: Bullet: '5.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid "Repeat from step 3 for every control point you want to delete."
msgstr "削除したい調整点すべてで上記の 3 ステップを繰り返します。"

#. type: Bullet: '6.  '
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"When done, you can either click anywhere outside the region, or press either "
"the **return** or **esc** (escape) key."
msgstr "完了したら、領域の外をクリックするか、**Return** または **ESC** キーを押します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: Regions-Deleting_Point.markdown.txt:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Note:** If you have a multi-button mouse, you can alternatively\n"
"right-click to pop-up the menu rather than control-click.\n"
msgstr "**註:** マルチボタンのマウスを使っている場合、Ctrl-クリックの代わりに右クリックでもポップアップを表示させられます。\n"
